## Users Request Collection [/user]

### Get current user [GET]

This request needed only for test.

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "UserName": "SomeUserName",
            "Email": "some_email@gmail.com",
            "AuthToken": "some_long_long_token"
        }
        
## Token Request Collection [/auth]

### Is valid token [POST]

Is this auth token valid

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "token": "token"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /token

    + Body

            {
                "token": "new_token"
            }

## Authorize Request Collection [/authorize]

### Authorize [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "UserName": "name",
            "Email": "email",
            "Password": "Password",
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /token

    + Body

            {
                "token": "new_token"
            }